hands_on_practices.solution:
我们希望计算复合时期的共动相干尺度，
$$\xi_{rec}=\frac{L(t_{rec})}{a_{rec}}\,,\qquad a_{rec}=\frac1{1+z_{rec}}\,. $$
由于级串在物质-辐射相等时停止，所以 $L(t_{rec})=L(t_{eq})$。在辐射时期
$$\frac{dL}{dt}=c_S\,v_A,\quad v_A^2\approx\frac{2\rho_B}{w}\approx\frac{2\rho_B}{\tfrac43\rho_r}
=\frac32\frac{\rho_B}{\rho_r}\,. $$
但 $\rho_B\propto a^{-4}$ 且 $\rho_r\propto a^{-4}$，所以 
$$\frac{\rho_B}{\rho_r}=\frac{\Omega_{B,0}}{\Omega_{r,0}}\quad\Rightarrow\quad
v_A=\sqrt{\frac32\,\frac{\Omega_{B,0}}{\Omega_{r,0}}}\equiv\text{const.}$$
因此
$$L(t)=c_S\,v_A\,t\,,\quad L(t_{eq})=c_S\,\sqrt{\frac32\frac{\Omega_{B,0}}{\Omega_{r,0}}}\;t_{eq}\,. $$
在辐射主导阶段 $H(a)=H_0\sqrt{\Omega_{r,0}}\,a^{-2}$，所以
$$t_{eq}\simeq\frac1{2H(a_{eq})}
=\frac{a_{eq}^2}{2H_0\sqrt{\Omega_{r,0}}},\qquad a_{eq}=\frac{\Omega_{r,0}}{\Omega_{m,0}}\,. $$
于是
$$t_{eq}=\frac{\Omega_{r,0}^2}{2H_0\sqrt{\Omega_{r,0}}\,\Omega_{m,0}^2}
=\frac{\Omega_{r,0}^{3/2}}{2H_0\,\Omega_{m,0}^2}\,. $$
因此
\begin{align*}
L(t_{eq})
=c_S\sqrt{\frac32\frac{\Omega_{B,0}}{\Omega_{r,0}}}
\;\frac{\Omega_{r,0}^{3/2}}{2H_0\,\Omega_{m,0}^2}
=c_S\frac{\sqrt{\tfrac32}\,\sqrt{\Omega_{B,0}}\,\Omega_{r,0}}{2H_0\,\Omega_{m,0}^2}\,.
\end{align*}
最后
$$\xi_{rec}=\frac{L(t_{eq})}{a_{rec}}
=L(t_{eq})\,(1+z_{rec})
=\frac{c_S\,\sqrt{\tfrac32}\,\Omega_{r,0}\,\sqrt{\Omega_{B,0}}\,(1+z_{rec})}
{2\,H_0\,\Omega_{m,0}^2}\,. $$
